data.description: Welcome to Linwood! Enjoy the quiet living and cheaper taxes! This home, situated on a sizable parcel, is mere minutes from town and offers a peaceful country life. The kitchen is full of cabinets and is complimented lots of counter space for serving Sunday brunches in the dinette. The large deck in the back yard is well shaded and is perfect for those summer and fall grill outs. The yard is spacious at .66 acres and has the potential for some serious gardening. The living room features large windows that offer bright lighting and the stone walled fireplace will make the whole home cozy on those snowy days. If you have some toys to store or have been searching for a workshop space, check out the detached garage. If golfing is your thing, the Wisconsin River Golf Course is located right off the front porch. This home is perfect for the the first time home buyers or those that are looking to start a family. Call now to schedule your private showing.,Seller represents that propane tank is leased through L and L Propane. New R21 Insulation on first floor, new fire place hearth, drywall updates on first floor, plumbing has been updated with PEX, Owned water softener system and pressure tank and jet pump for well in 2020, New sump pump and all lights are converted to LED. Large window in living room is new also.
